data.title: Frank Iero
data.meta_description: Frank Iero. Soundtrack: Senza freni. Frank Iero was born on 31 October 1981 in Belleville, New Jersey, USA. He is an actor and composer, known for Senza freni (2012), Never Back Down - Mai arrendersi (2008) and L'uomo con i pugni di ferro (2012). He has been married to Jamia Nestor since 9 March 2008. They have three children.
data.text:
He was the lead singer for the band Pencey Prep. They disbanded in 2002. He was front-man to a band called Leathermouth for a while as a side project to My Chemical Romance. My Chemical Romance Broke up On announced its break-up on March 22, 2013, one month after the final release in the Conventional Weapons series.

Frank has also played in the bands Hybrid, Sector 12, I am a Graveyard, Death Spells, and briefly with Give Up The Ghost.
